
Star Wars
~~~~~~~~~

      With this game, the Star Wars universe comes alive as the Rebel
Alliance battles against the unrelenting power of the Galactic Empire. You
have the power to control, alter and feel the Force.

      Each starter pack contains 60 randomly assorted cards (30 dark side
and 30 light side) so with two starter packs you can customize Rebel and
Imperial decks and master the amazing powers of the Force. 


   Limited Editions
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   Star Wars Starter Pack.................................£5.99
   Star Wars Boosters.....................................£2.25

   UltraPro Deck Protectors (100 in a pack)...............£5.50
    (To store and protect your cards both in and out of play)

   Resealable write-on polythene bags.....................£0.10
    (Ideal to store one starter pack)



      In order to start, you need a minimum of 1 starter deck per player
but you can add as many Boosters to your deck as you like.
